Map Trivy findings to HIPAA requirements:
- Exposed secrets → 164.312(a)(1) Access Control (unique user identification)
- Vulnerable dependencies → 164.308(a)(5)(ii)(B) Protection from Malicious Software
- Container misconfigurations → 164.312(a)(1) Access Control
- IaC misconfigurations → 164.312(a)(2)(iv) Encryption, 164.312(e) Transmission Security

